      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Ur-Ninĝirsu , ruler of Lagaš , son of Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of Ninĝirsu's E-ninnu , fashioned this ( door socket ) ."
